briefdescription.para: Load resource from stream. May be called from a worker thread. Return true if successful.

briefdescription.para: Return a new instance of a decoder sound stream. Used by compressed sounds.

detaileddescription.para: Return default frequency as a float. BIND_AS_PROPERTY

briefdescription.para: Return default frequency as an integer.

detaileddescription.para: Return whether data is sixteen bit. BIND_AS_PROPERTY
Return whether data is stereo. BIND_AS_PROPERTY

briefdescription.para: Fix interpolation by copying data from loop start to loop end (looped), or adding silence (oneshot). Called internally, does not normally need to be called, unless the sound data is modified manually on the fly.
Load optional parameters from an XML file.
